    "33639450": {
      "title": "Fine structure of detached coils observed by micro-CT",
      "abstract": "Detached GDC was observed by high resolutional industrial microCT, whose resolution was higher than 0.1 mm. Unexpected destruction of the coils (kinking) was detected and unraveling also clearly visualized. Much higher resolution can improve safe and effectivity of GDC procedure."
